{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"女人做事就是这样子的，总以为自己做得很聪明很神勇，如果有个女人真的能做出一件让男人佩服的事来，那么这个女人恐怕就不是一个女人。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":10,"line_start":28,"line_end":28},{"speaker":"char_gong_ping","speaker_name":"宫萍","listener":"char_lu_xiao_feng","text":"刚才你在说什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"刚才我在说什么？我什么都没有说啊。","tone":"疑问","chapter":10,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"刚才我只不过好像放了个屁而已。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_lao_ban_niang","speaker_name":"老板娘","listener":"char_lu_xiao_feng","text":"柳乘风不但是你的朋友，也是我们的朋友，他死得太冤，我们也和你一样，想找出杀他的凶手，为他复仇。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":97,"line_end":97},{"speaker":"char_lao_ban_niang","speaker_name":"老板娘","listener":"char_lu_xiao_feng","text":"沙大户、赵瞎子、许老大、宫素素，和我这个不争气的老公，都可能是杀死柳乘风的人。今天你在沙大户的床上看到我，就因为我一直都想把他捉来问个清楚。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":105,"line_end":105},{"speaker":"char_lao_ban_niang","speaker_name":"老板娘","listener":"char_lu_xiao_feng","text":"我相信你一定也明白，要捉沙大户这种人，只有先上他的床。","tone":"无奈","chapter":10,"line_start":107,"line_end":107},{"speaker":"char_xiao_jiao_hua","speaker_name":"小叫化","listener":"char_lu_xiao_feng","text":"只要一上床，万事都风凉，连沙大户都上了当，何况这个老王八蛋？","tone":"调侃","chapter":10,"line_start":111,"line_end":111},{"speaker":"char_xiao_jiao_hua","speaker_name":"小叫化","listener":"char_lu_xiao_feng","text":"我对付这两个老太婆的情况虽然有点不一样，多多少少还是用了一点美男计。","tone":"调侃","chapter":10,"line_start":115,"line_end":115},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"老实说，我这一生经过的危险实在不少，有很多次的确是差一点就完蛋了，可是最危险的一次，还是那一次。","tone":"认真","chapter":10,"line_start":133,"line_end":133},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"因为那时候我实在没想到宫萍和老板娘会杀我，更没有想到她们的出手居然那么狠毒。如果现在你要我在江湖中例举几个武功最高最可怕的女人，我还是会把她们两个人算在里面，因为直到现在为止，江湖中能胜过她们的女人实在不多。","tone":"陈述","chapter":10,"line_start":135,"line_end":135}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_lu_xiao_feng","name":"陆小凤","alias":[],"identity":"江湖名人","faction":null,"role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"江湖传奇人物，四条眉毛的陆小凤","personality":{"traits":["机智","幽默","重情义","风流","机敏","豁达"],"speech_style":"轻松幽默，带有调侃意味","temperament":"随性洒脱"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":10,"line_end":10,"text":"陆小凤非但连一点好笑的意思都没有"}]},{"id":"char_gong_ping","name":"宫萍","alias":[],"identity":"可疑人物之一","faction":null,"role":"companion","archetype":"assassin","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"紫裙老妪的真面目，实为年轻女子","personality":{"traits":["冷静","果断","狠辣","精明","隐忍","果断"],"speech_style":"慢吞吞，不急不躁","temperament":"沉稳内敛"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":18,"line_end":18,"text":"宫萍根本没有过去看"}]},{"id":"char_lao_ban_niang","name":"老板娘","alias":[],"identity":"柳乘风之友","faction":null,"role":"companion","archetype":"assassin","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"表面上是老板娘，实为武功高手","personality":{"traits":["精明","狠辣","善于伪装","果断","有手段"],"speech_style":"直言不讳","temperament":"外柔内刚"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":69,"line_end":69,"text":"开门的居然是老板娘"}]},{"id":"char_xiao_jiao_hua","name":"小叫化","alias":[],"identity":"柳乘风之友","faction":null,"role":"companion","archetype":"assassin","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"看似乞丐实为高手","personality":{"traits":["狡黠","风趣","机智","善于伪装","胆大"],"speech_style":"调侃戏谑","temperament":"玩世不恭"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[10],"source_refs":[{"chapter":10,"line_start":77,"line_end":77,"text":"陆小凤第一眼看见的就是那个小王八蛋"}]},{"id":"char_sha_da_hu","name":"沙大户","alias":[],"identity":"凶手嫌疑人之一","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"财雄势大的地方豪强","personality"